name: Weequay Skiff Master
Lore: 'Many of the Weequay at Jabba''s palace work for Barada. Enjoy racing their skiffs. Dislike the Nikto guards at Jabba''s palace.',
Text: 'Deploys only on Tatooine. Power +2 When defending a battle or when with another Weequay in battle. Adds 3 to power of any Skiff he drives.',
